# Python Example Rules

- IFactory is mandatory — implement all 5 methods
- Use `parse_common_args()` — no custom argparse
- 4 variants: `_sync.py`, `_async.py`, `_sync_cpp_postprocess.py`, `_async_cpp_postprocess.py`
- sys.path insertion pattern for imports
- Every model dir needs `config.json` and `__init__.py`
- Read `.deepx/skills/dx-build-python-app.md` for full patterns
